{
  "_schema": "scope-registry v2",
  "_docs": "See memory/contract.md \u00a75-\u00a77 and memory/ADR-001-scope-coverage.md. Curator maintains this file. Special agent ids: '*' = any agent, '_user' = interactive user, '_curator' = designated curator agent (resolved via curator_agents list). Coverage map: memory/scope-coverage.md.",
